{"tid":421923,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好掛住中秋節時落公園玩燈籠蠟燭？","createTime":"2017-10-02T15:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T00:15:37.000Z","uid":102938,"like":96,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"6965879da8084e85766eea19fd205186cd29bd89","tid":421923,"uid":102938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:36:31.000Z","msg":"小學至初中，中秋節果陣都會同朋友落樓下公園玩燈籠蠟燭<br />\n果陣中秋氣氛係好濃厚，記得中秋節正日前後一星期，樓下公園好多人玩<br />\n最勁係仲記得係完左中秋節半個月後既星期六都仲有人玩蠟燭<br />\n但現在，即使夜晚望見樓下公園有人玩燈籠，但都只係寥寥無幾<br />\n蠟燭暫時都係沒人玩，所以真係好掛住以前中秋節落公園玩燈籠蠟燭<br />\n回憶起果一種中秋節氣氛真係十分濃厚&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n唔知有無巴絲都同我一樣，好想組番幾個朋友一齊玩呢？"},{"pid":"174927fa3a2829524b49e97555b5b7c3cd206870","tid":421923,"uid":75694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"依家個個落公園捉仆街mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa6b2d12b096ff52b53ad58c8e9494c6c41c0ce","tid":421923,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:39:24.000Z","msg":"通常執人地掉左果d玩"},{"pid":"b33894f8d8a0da2f4733ee601a366d985f5b31a6","tid":421923,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:45:49.000Z","msg":"以前公屋公園 天台週圍都係細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e4e0e2c94e5a74e48f045a5ae4582d692161b3","tid":421923,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:46:53.000Z","msg":"好鍾意中秋節<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06958c514cc46f18af93ac3a0d8c0d57228670c9","tid":421923,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:46:55.000Z","msg":"下...你幾耐無出街?中秋節公園不嬲大撚把人玩蠟燭"},{"pid":"f94b594437ec66bc5a72d3a1d0a47218f4b8d2a9","tid":421923,"uid":102938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:50:10.000Z","msg":"近大半年開始少左好多人玩pokemon，個熱潮都幾快完<br />\n另外真係近幾年開始已經愈來愈少人玩蠟燭燈籠，唔係話無<br />\n最多都係正日，一完左正日，就好少人玩<br />\n但以前中秋節（約十年或之前啦）係正日前後一星期都大把人玩"},{"pid":"5675f7c09890461c0a50d64729f7c001e069686a","tid":421923,"uid":57227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:52:53.000Z","msg":"2000年左右，勁多細佬提早煲蠟"},{"pid":"44c9efc47d9c1dff0cf9dac33332be3b3b2f9900","tid":421923,"uid":62286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"同一區嘅人都長大了，自然少小朋友。可能新區會好少少。 <br />\n<br />\n不過社會係變咗，香港今時唔同往日。"},{"pid":"461acef69362e135f4bf76fe192dc61993315b9f","tid":421923,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:12:31.000Z","msg":"一路食飯一路聽到樓下啫啫聲又有火光反射，嗱嗱淋食完飯落去睇熱鬧食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5ab747637a37740842baadec58382ccf92d0da","tid":421923,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:45:42.000Z","msg":"曾幾何時 我都係中秋既參與者 而家只係旁觀者"},{"pid":"a4251ad7ed542fb3ce1f6e08b808902b0a54a6e3","tid":421923,"uid":136637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:23:52.000Z","msg":"我而家都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日覺得自己長不大 成個細路咁"},{"pid":"8f54651f6dec6a65478857a93f3111330e2f03af","tid":421923,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:49:24.000Z","msg":"都好 唔會燒到自己"},{"pid":"e626adfa51f1e7f5fe9861976df67be596bcd0ee","tid":421923,"uid":8514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T19:50:31.000Z","msg":"好想煲蠟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30be03f55ce6e3291445dd9f742c0b94ae5ad2d4","tid":421923,"uid":118041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:18:55.000Z","msg":"前年係公園玩，畀個仆街呀婆食住煙來投訴我點蠟燭。然後成堆保安衝出來叫我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我之後轉咗去村屋玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr